<!--||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||
								SHIP ICONS
||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||||-->

<mod:findLike type="ships" limit="1">
	<mod:findLike type="shipIcons" limit="1">
		<mod-append:shipIcon>
			<name>icon_co_ravager_auto</name>
			<tooltip>RAVAGER'S OPERATING SYSTEM:
This enemy is automated, meaning it can't be crew-killed. This machine's "mind" forces its systems act as though the are manned by crew with 1 lvl skills, and repaires will be made automatically. Breaches will prevent repairs in the affected room. Not for long.</tooltip>
		</mod-append:shipIcon>
		<mod-append:shipIcon>
			<name>icon_co_ravager_plating</name>
			<tooltip>RAVAGER PLATING:
This enemy's hull plating automatically patches breaches and puts out fires very fast.</tooltip>
		</mod-append:shipIcon>
		<mod-append:shipIcon>
			<name>icon_co_ravager_protocol</name>
			<tooltip>RAVAGER'S DEVASTETING PROTOCOLS:
"They're just machines... soulless, cruel, without any feelings or desires, just machines. Aren't they?"
All enemy crew become susceptible to suffocation, while all onboard drones are absorbed by the ship's hull, offering no resistance.</tooltip>
		</mod-append:shipIcon>
		<mod-append:shipIcon>
			<name>icon_co_ravager_shield</name>
			<tooltip>RAVAGER SHIELDING:
This enemy is protected by an Energy Shield. Hacking, Mind Control, Teleportation, Boarding Drones, and all hull-damaging or ion weapons will all be blocked until disabled.
This Energy Shield regenerates over time while the shield system is active. Enemy crew can no longer return to their ship if they teleport to a ship with this shielding installed.</tooltip>
		</mod-append:shipIcon>
		
		<mod-append:shipIcon>
			<name>icon_co_ravager_lab_targeting</name>
			<tooltip>TARGET FOCUSING:
This enemy's Stage II Ravagers are able to mark a priority target for death, killing your crew members one by one.</tooltip>
		</mod-append:shipIcon>
	</mod:findLike>
</mod:findLike>


